  { name: 'Food Bucket List', description: 'Journal Foodie, Amus-Bouche, Small Plates Tapa, Gift for a Top Chef Recipes, and Meals', price: 25, image:"", sku: "bucket_01" },
  { name: 'Foot hammock', description: 'This must be a dream. Barefoot … in a hammock … at work. Does it get any cooler than this? Who says relaxation and hard work can’t go hand in hand?', price: 30, image: "", sku: "foot_hummock_01"},
  { name: 'The Walk By Scrabble Board', description: 'Show them who’s boss…but not too obviously, of course. Wreak passive-aggressive havoc with this walk-by game board.', price: 20, image: "", sku: "scrabble_01"},
  { name: 'Lego coffee mug', description: 'Everyone gets their best ideas when in the throes of a caffeine rush, but the tools aren’t always handy just then to construct their timeless masterpiece. ', price: 20, image:"", sku: "legomug_01"},
  { name: 'Guzzle buddy wine glass', description: 'Anyone who tells you that you can’t look classy drinking straight out of the bottle simply lacks imagination. And they clearly haven’t seen one of these. ', price: 20, image: "", sku: "glass_01"},
  { name: 'The subtle art of not Giving a fuck', description: 'Mark Manson seriously doesn’t give a f*ck, and he wants you to not give a f*ck too. Despite its (not so subtle) title, this book isn’t about not caring. It’s about not caring about the things that don’t matter', price: 20, image:"", sku: "book_01" },
  { name: 'Never have I ever game', description:'Help them learn more about the people around them than they could ever possibly want to know with the classic party game Never Have I Ever.', price: 25, image:"", sku: "cards_02"},
  { name: 'Bring me wine socks', description:'Generally speaking, the last person in the room who needs more wine is the person who’s already gone feet up.', price: 10, image:"", sku: "beersocks_02"},
  { name: 'Fujifilm Instax Mini 9 Instant Camera', description: "The Fujifilm Instax Mini instant camera is a must-have for that friend who constantly loves to snap photos, and now the pics don't have to sit in their camera roll! It comes in vibrant light blue, dark blue, green, pink, and smokey white, so you can pick the color that matches her personality.", price: 56, image:"", sku: "Fujifilm_01"},
  { name: 'Echo Smart Speaker (2nd Generation)', description: "The Amazon Echo is a perfect gift to give friends and family who haven't yet experienced connected home products. Compact and incredibly smart (it's powered by the retail giant's excellent Alexa smart home platform), this second-generation gadget takes voice commands ranging from ordering more detergent, playing music, calling Uber, and so much more.", price: 120, image:"", sku: "Echo_01"},
  { name: "Reindeer Christmas T-Shirt", description: "We all have that one person on our list who's literally impossible to shop for. When all of your traditional gift go-tos won't do, get them a T-shirt that's equally as fun and festive as an ugly Christmas sweater (except they'll actually want to wear it!).", price: 25, image:"", sku: "T-Shirt_01"},
  { name: "Eberjey Women's Gisele Two-Piece Pajama Set", description: "If you know someone who loves nothing more than to cuddle into the comforters and flip on some Netflix to genuinely chill, this luxe pajama set by Eberjey will make her heart skip a beat!", price: 120, image:"", sku: "Pajama_01"},
  { name: "De'Longhi Nespresso Lattissima Espresso Machine", description: "This seriously stylish espresso machine is a perfect gift idea for the connoisseur who could use some perking up right at home. Complete with a milk frother, this espresso maker is on Oprah's list of favorite things this year. Who wouldn't want to whip up a mouthwatering latte in just 40 seconds?", price: 379, image:"", sku: "Nespresso_01"},
  { name: "Diptyque Votive Candle Trio: Baies, Figuier, Roses", description: "Treat the most generous person you know to this premium mini-candle trio. It includes the best-selling Baies, Figuier, and Roses scents — three intoxicating blends that add a little glam to even the most mundane day.", price: 149, image:"", sku: "Candle_01"},
  { name: "Jabra Elite Wireless Earbuds and Charging Case", description: "The Jabra Elite 65t are the best completely wireless earbuds on the market today, and any tech-savvy person will love to unwrap these underneath the tree! They're stylish, comfy, and capable of delivering an excellent audio experience, no matter what kind of tunes they love. From listening to music to seamlessly taking calls on the go, you can't top these truly wireless earbuds.", price: 163, image:"", sku: "Earbuds_01"},
  { name: "Hatchimals HatchiBabies", description: "This year, Hatchimals released a new toy. Your kid can hatch an enchanting baby creature — in a diaper. If you're cool with associating blue with the male gender and pink and purple with the female gender in your house, then you might as well throw a mini gender-reveal party while the egg hatches, since that's the theme!", price: 60, image:"", sku: "Hatchimal_01"},
  { name: "Ring Wi-Fi Enabled Video Doorbell", description: "Every homeowner needs one of these insanely popular smart doorbells. It's simple to set up, and once it is, it makes it easy to check in on your home from afar thanks to the on-demand video stream which syncs to your smartphone. Ring Doorbell even works with Alexa, so you can speak to the delivery guy whether you're upstairs in your home, or out at the grocery store, letting them know it's fine to leave a package!", price: 100, image:"", sku: "Doorbell_01"},
  { name: "Christmas Pajamas Long-Sleeve T-Shirt", description: "Pick up a long-sleeved tee for every member of your Christmas crew, and gather around the tree for a festive family pick (after presents, of course!).", price: 30, image:"", sku: "Pajama_02"},
  { name: "Amazon Fire TV Cube", description: "With built-in Alexa and several microphones, the Amazon Fire device is designed for those who often lose the remote (or are just too lazy to press a button). All your favorite couch potato will have to do is muster up the energy to mutter, 'Alexa, play Game of Thrones.' How cool is that?!  It's compatible with all major streaming devices like Netflix, Hulu, and Prime Video, so your lucky friend or family member will never miss their favorite shows.", price: 120, image:"", sku: "Amazon_01"},
  { name: "WowWee Fingerlings Monkey and Mini BFF", description: "These cute interactive monkeys were in high demand last year, and they just keep getting more and more popular in 2018. What kid (or honestly, adult) wouldn't want a funky monkey hanging off of their finger? This fingerling monkey uses sensors to interact with people — how cool is that? This fingerling comes with a mini BFF too, for double the fun!", price: 15, image:"", sku: "Fingerling_01"},
  { name: "Lagostina Giada Stainless Steel Dutch Oven with Copper Lid", description: "From succulent chuck roasts, to rich sauces and soups, there's nothing your favorite chef can't cook in this chic Dutch oven pot. Its tri-ply copper bonded base distributes heat quickly and evenly, while a stylish hammered lid locks in moisture and bold flavors. Best of all, it's oven- and broiler-safe, so they can feel free to get creative with their cooking style.", price: 80, image:"", sku: "Oven_01"},
  { name: "L.O.L. Surprise! Confetti Pop-Series 3", description: "If your little ones love a good surprise, they'll get a kick out of peeling away the seven layers of this pack, filled with a secret message, emoji stickers, an outfit, accessories, and more. At its core, one of 45 collectible L.O.L. Lil Outrageous Surprise dolls is ready to play, featuring a unique special action, like crying, peeing, and even changing color.", price: 24, image:"", sku: "Collectible_01"},
  { name: "Nintendo Switch With Neon Blue and Neon Red Joy-Con", description: "The Nintendo Switch can transition from a mobile gaming device to a home gaming console by simply docking it into a station. The joy-con controllers can take their gaming experience to a whole new level. Playing on the go will get a serious upgrade when you gift this!", price: 300, image:"", sku: "Nintendo_01"},
  { name: "Scruff-a-Luvs Mystery Rescue Pet", description: "Find a pet so scruffy, and make it fluffy! This super cute toy is already predicted to be a huge hit with kids for the holidays, so you might as well stock up while you can for all the little ones on your list this year. Each pet comes in a matted ball you have to wash and dry to reveal which one you've adopted. Seriously, how cute is this?", price: 34, image:"", sku: "Pet_01"},
  { name: "Fitbit Charge 3", description: "The Fitbit Charge 3 is a water-resistant, user-friendly fitness tracker anyone in your life will love. The gadget features continuous heart-rate tracking, GPS, a handy touchscreen, and swappable wristbands. In addition to tracking health data and delivering smartphone notifications, the tracker can also help users unwind via personalized breathing exercises. We love the host of fitness-tracking programs and extended battery life this updated version comes with. Gift it to your fit friend who deserves an upgrade!", price: 150, image:"", sku: "Fitbit_01"},
  { name: "KitchenAid Artisan Design Stand Mixer With Glass Bowl", description: "Baking just got way better. This stunning stand mixer by KitchenAid is part of their artisan design series, and it includes a mod glass mixing bowl.", price: 364, image:"", sku: "Mixer_01"},
  { name: "Amazon Echo Dot (3rd Generation)", description: "The new Dot is here, and it's 70% louder than previous models. Plus, it flaunts a nicer, rounder design with a fabric-bound speaker. The Echo Dot will hear your voice commands via seven built-in microphones.", price: 50, image:"", sku: "Amazon_02"},
  { name: "Lucky Bums Toddler Pull Sled", description: "Do you know a little one who doesn't want to miss out on any of the action in the snow? This Lucky Bums sled makes it possible for even the tiny tots to jump in on the fun. Strap them right in and pull right through the fluffy snow! By next year, they'll be ready to take on the sleds with the big kids.", price: 64, image: "", sku: "Sled_01"},
  { name: "Alesis Surge Mesh Kit Electronic Drum Kit", description: "If your recipient is hoping to break out as the next Ringo Starr, this impressive electronic drum kit will help them hit every beat. All eight pieces collectively create superior sound, and an included surge drum module will give your musician all of the tools to become a pro player.", price: 500, image: "", sku: "Drum_01"},
  { name: "Instant Pot 9-in-1 Multi-Functional Pressure Cooker", description: "It might look like an average pressure cooker, but there are several surprising functions they can take advantage of with this appliance (like making yogurt!). Some other roles this appliance can take on? It's also a slow cooker, rice cooker, egg cooker, steamer, warmer, sterilizer, and cake maker.", price: 130, image: "", sku: "Pot_01"},
  { name: "Roku Express+ Streaming Stick", description: "A lot comes in a little package with the Roku Express+ streaming stick. This streaming service is easy to set up, and it provides access to over 350,000 shows and movies across paid and free channels, like Hulu, Netflix, and PBS Kids. The best part? They'll have smart TV access without any monthly subscription fees.", price: 42, image: "", sku: "Roku_01"},
  { name: "NutriBullet Balance: Bluetooth Enabled Smart Blender", description: "It's so easy to whip up a nutritious smoothie with a NutriBullet! Gift it to your friend who's determined to start 2019 off the right way — with a healthy breakfast. Plus, this new version is updated with Bluetooth, so you can stay connected and make prep time even easier and pull info on the nutritional value of your smoothie.", price: 125, image: "", sku: "Blender_01"},
  { name: "CHI Ceramic and Titanium Hairstyling Iron", description: "A favorite among beauty gurus, bloggers, and style newbies alike, this straightening iron boasts titanium-infused ceramic plates that create silky strands with a lot of shine. Gone are the days of fried, staticky hair! Trust us, any beauty lover will want this", price: 130, image: "", sku: "Iron_01"},
  { name: "Amazon Echo Show (2nd Generation)", description: "With a larger 10-inch touchscreen than the previous version, a 5 MP camera, and eight built-in microphones, the newly improved Amazon Echo Show smart speaker adds a fresh way of interacting with Alexa. In addition to playing tunes, managing the daily routine, and controlling your connected home, the Amazon Echo Show can play videos, too.", price: 230, image: "", sku: "Amazon_03"},
  { name: "Tile Pro with Replaceable Battery", description: "For the friend who can't keep track of everything, the upgraded Tile Pro makes the perfect gift! This tiny, trendy tracker can attach to just about anything. Plus, it connects to an item-finding app, so your friend will have instant access to the largest lost-and-found community so she can find what's missing in a pinch. The replaceable battery will need to be changed only after a full year of use.", price: 60, image: "", sku: "Tile_01"},
  { name: "Dyson Ball Multi Floor Upright Corded Vacuum", description: "The holidays are a great time to gift that big-ticket item that's been on their list for a while, and this Dyson vacuum is a top-of-the-line pick any household will appreciate. This vacuum is perfect for cleaning across a wide variety of carpets and hard flooring. Plus, thanks to the suction wand, they can efficiently deep-clean their whole house, from under furniture to up high to get those pesky ceiling-fan blades. It's the perfect gift for a true neat freak!", price: 250, image: "", sku: "Dyson_01"},
  { name: "Party Popteenies Surprise Set With Confetti", description: "These adorable Popteenie dolls are always ready for a party with a pull-twist-and-pop feature that’ll surprise your little one with a burst of festive confetti. Inclusive of more than 25 collectable fashion pieces and party accessories — including three dolls — gifting this set is a great way to complete any upcoming holiday celebration.", price: 20, image: "", sku: "Popteenies_01"},
  { name: "littleBits Avengers Hero Inventor Kit", description: "We all know a kid who can't get enough of all things Marvel, and this hot toy of 2018 is 100% worth the splurge. It's perfect for serious superheroes who are ready to train and try different powers like night vision, light powers, and more.", price: 150, image: "", sku: "Avengers_01"},
  { name: "Oster Rechargeable and Cordless Wine Opener with Chiller", description: "Say goodbye to trapped corks with a cordless wine opener that'll have your recipient sipping faster. White-wine drinkers will particularly love the included stainless steel chiller for its double-wall construction that'll keep bottles cool through hours of conversation. For extra points, consider complementing this gift with a stellar bottle of wine.", price: 30, image: "", sku: "Wine_01"},
  { name: "Amazon Fire HD 8 Kindle", description: "Amazon's Fire HD Kindle is the perfect gift for friends and family who are avid readers and don't want to carry print editions everywhere they go. The e-reader has a sharp display with adjustable lighting, a lightweight body with excellent build quality, Wi-Fi connectivity, and a battery that can last for weeks on a single charge.", price: 80, image: "", sku: "Amazon_04"},
  { name: "You Are a Badass 2019 Day-to-Day Calendar", description: "If you have a friend who never seems to “turn off,” this might be the perfect calendar to gift her ahead of 2019. Based on Jen Sincero's best-selling You Are a Badass book, this calendar was designed to give her a boost on the days when she's feeling less than badass.", price: 15, image: "", sku: "Calendar_04"},
  { name: "Sonos Beam Soundbar with Amazon Alexa Voice Control", description: "This sound bar is perfect for people who love to experience TV and sound to their full effect. It features Alexa voice control as well, so they can use it to listen to music, control smart tools in the home, or check on the weather.", price: 400, image: "", sku: "Sonos_01"},
  { name: "Salt, Fat, Acid, Heat: Mastering the Elements of Good Cooking by Samin Nosrat", description: "This New York Times bestseller and recent winner of the 2018 James Beard Award for Best General Cookbook will inspire any at-home chef. Salt, Fat, Acid, Heat will fuel the fire under their pan with a newfound appreciation of food science and the art and joy of cooking.", price: 35, image: "", sku: "Cookbook_01"},
  { name: "Instant Pot Ace 60 Cooking Blender", description: "This brand new appliance from Instant Pot features eight smart blending programs and settings with heat for whipping up soups and milks. The glass blending jar is a breeze to clean, and the motor is hushed so the entire house won't wake when the morning smoothie is blending. Gift this innovative blender to the new homeowner — or the chef who needs fresh inspiration to roll their sleeves up in the kitchen again!", price: 99, image: "", sku: "Blender_02"},
  { name: "KitchenAid Electric Kettle", description: "This retro kettle from KitchenAid is striking in twilight blue, and it'll definitely jazz up anyone's stovetop. They'll love the sleek design and vibrant color, and be sure to pair it with one of the best teas!", price: 70, image: "", sku: "Kettle_01"},
  { name: "Mackage Women's Cano Gloves", description: "These leather gloves with a cashmere lining are perfect for your most fashionable friend. Both fun and functional, they'll keep her warm without sacrificing any style points.", price: 156, image: "", sku: "Gloves_01"},
  { name: "Advanced Mixology Moscow Mule Copper Mugs Gift Set", description: "This set of four copper mugs features a classic hammered finish and a shine that'll make them stand out at any party! The set also includes copper straws, coasters, and a shot glass for a complete party package.", price: 60, image: "", sku: "Mug_01"},
  { name: "Delish: Eat Like Every Day’s the Weekend", description: "Do you know someone who would think nothing (or actually, everything) of whipping up a whopping serving of grilled cheese sticks? Or what about baking up a batch of mint chip brownie cups in a muffin tin? Yep — this cookbook by the edit staff at Delish provides tons of recipes that will push comfort-food cooking to the next level.", price: 30, image: "", sku: "Cookbook_02"},
  { name: "Smeg Kettle", description: "It's like a piece of jewelry for the kitchen counter! These kettles are so stylish, and there are seven colors available. We love the auto-shutoff function, too.", price: 150, image: "", sku: "Kettle_02"},
  { name: "The Orb Factory Orb Molecules Merkitty", description: "This funky toy contains 'atoms' that kids can squish between their fingers to mold new figures. The orb molecules bond together to build new creations, and they can be reused for new inventions over and over again.", price: 14, image: "", sku: "Merkitty_01"},
  { name: "J.A. Henckels International Statement Knife Block Set", description: "This versatile 15-piece knife set will provide quality cuts for a novice or experienced chef. Made of stainless steel, these knives (and the sturdy wood block) will last them a lifetime.", price: 130, image: "", sku: "Knife_01"},
  { name: "Bark Box Subscription", description: "Make a special little woofer extra happy this year! Order a subscription to Bark Box to receive a new load of toys, treats, and gifts every month. There's a new theme in every shipment, and the boxes are customized based on your dog's size. You didn't think Santa Paws forgot about him, did you?", price: 20, image: "", sku: "Box_01"},
  { name: "Soda Stream", description: "This soda maker is perfect for the health-conscious friend who loves to sip on something fizzy. Plus, the appliance is slim and won't take up too much room! Switch up the flavors for even more inspiration to get in that daily dose of H2O.", price: 107, image: "", sku: "Soda_01"},
  { name: "Bodum Bistro Burr Grinder", description: "Know someone who's crazy for java? They'll seriously never forget it when you gift this stunning Bodum Bistro coffee grinder. Get ready for a big inhalation, because the smell of freshly ground coffee is addicting.", price: 150, image: "", sku: "Grinder_01"},
  { name: "Beachwaver Curling Iron", description: "This curling iron is the one that the pros use behind the scenes at the Victoria's Secret fashion show. It magically creates the perfect beach waves that are laid-back and sexy. If you know a gal who loves the look, she'll love you for life if you give her this.", price: 129, image: "", sku: "Iron_02"},
  { name: "Dash Compact Air Fryer", description: "By using air rather than oil, this kitchen appliance will cut back on fat by 75%, so they can grill, steam, and fry everything from Brussels sprouts to french fries. We love this aqua color, but this compact model is also available in black, gray, red, or white for a trendy touch to any kitchen.", price: 60, image: "", sku: "Fryer_01"},
  { name: "LUX Essentials Whiskey Diamonds", description: "Dazzle whiskey, wine, or cocktails with these diamonds that'll keep it cool without watering down that liquid gold. Punky in pink cosmos and handsome in bourbon-based cocktails, these stones will be a fantastic addition to anyone's home bar.", price: 17, image: "", sku: "Whiskey_01"},
  { name: "Leatherman Signal Multitool", description: "If you know someone with a reputation for fixing things up, give him a Leatherman multitool to add to his toolbox. He'll appreciate how easy it is to switch it up when he's working on a project that requires different tools to get the job done.", price: 110, image: "", sku: "Tool_01"}
]

